# InvestTrack - Investment Portfolio Management

A comprehensive investment portfolio management application built with Next.js, Supabase, and shadcn/ui.

## Features

- **User Authentication**: Secure login and registration
- **Dashboard Overview**: View your portfolio value, asset allocation, and performance
- **Asset Management**: Track stocks, ETFs, cryptocurrencies, and other investments
- **Real-time Market Data**: Get up-to-date prices from external APIs
- **Transaction Tracking**: Record buys, sells, dividends, and other transactions
- **Portfolio Analysis**: Visualize your investment performance and allocation
- **Financial Goals**: Set and track progress toward financial targets
- **Notifications**: Stay informed about important portfolio events
- **Admin Panel**: Manage users and system settings (for admin users)

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Node.js 18+ and npm
- Supabase account

